text: Oktyabrskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Oktyabrsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 977 as of 2010. There are 11 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Sterlitamak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Oktyabrskoye, Sterlitamaksky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
